{
  "stem": "9601.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I think he talked to the-- to feed the dog, and he used to-- he talked to the-- to the hired help.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, Tante Chaika ran out of money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tante Chaika had the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They paid him, you know, every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, bribery or blackmail?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have today, you want 100.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tomorrow, you know, demand 200.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it had to last seven days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And finally, somehow we survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't last seven days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a-- one of those windy days that blew away the snow from the fields.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And snows are plowed, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're not really made fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they're just big slabs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the fields over there are not one big [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, you have field-- property lines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they're about half a foot wide between each field, because they probably put a marker and use the field.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody had about an 8-inch piece of land.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the dividing line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And every time you hit a-- you know, when they plowed, they plow away from the dividing line, right?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it's like a-- a sloping-- and you walk on that frozen stuff.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Tante Chaika's a big woman, and she holding on-- holding on to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when she falls, guess who she falls on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not on the ground, she falls on me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, boy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went to Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Scastny.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we get there, and we figure it out what-- why it took seven days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He dug a hole for us in the pigsty.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He took off the floor, because the Czechs kept their pigs on wooden floors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Cleanliness and, I guess, whatever, better productivity, less diseases, less death, of sudden death of pigs, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
